data.description:
The elegance and tranquility in this home are bursting at the seams but you won’t be, because this home offers an amazing 4200 sq ft.  5 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms with one bedroom and bath downstairs.  Oversized bonus room, dining room featuring coffered ceilings and a study with a custom built wall length book case!   
Gourmet kitchen features granite countertops and double ovens.  Fully fenced yard with extended patio and screened porch! This home truly has it all!
